org.jinq.jpa.transform

Class LambdaParameterArgumentHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jinq.jpa.transform.LambdaParameterArgumentHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SymbExArgumentHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregateStreamLambdaArgumentHandler, GroupingLambdasArgumentHandler, OuterJoinOnLambdaArgumentHandler, SelectFromWhereLambdaArgumentHandler

    public class LambdaParameterArgumentHandler
extends Object
implements SymbExArgumentHandler
    Handles the lookup of parameters passed to a lambda. Parameters can be used to represent query parameters or references to the data stream. This class handles the lookup of a data stream of the result of a Select..From..Where query.
